  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Prolonged bracing reduces the rate of clubfoot recurrence. In addition to bracing length,
      other factors, including compliance with bracing, gender, age, severity of clubfoot deformity
      and family history contribute to clubfoot recurrence.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <overall_status>Active, not recruiting</overall_status>
  <start_date>May 2012</start_date>
